item.description:
I am happy to announce our 5th annual Yule celebration!!

Come join us to watch the semi-annual Battle of the Oak & Holly King, where the Oak King will once again claim supremacy (and kiss all the girls afterwards!) and enjoy a fabulous (as always) pot luck supper!

We will also continue with our tradition of doing a pagan yankee swap, and have everyone carve the Yule log for their wishes for the coming year.

We will be having the meet up at Kelly's place this year, which you will all LOVE, and it is much easier to get to & find then Priya's place, even though it is in the same town.

Please bring a pot luck dish (homemade is always preferred!) and a pagan-type gift in the range of $10.00- $15.00.

Tentative Schedule of Events will be as follows:

2:30- 3:30 Appetizers & Meet-n-Greet

3:30- 4:30 Battle of the Oak & Holly King

5:00- 6:00 Pot Luck Feast

6:00-Â 7:30 Pagan Yankee Swap

8:00- Dessert

Expect a ton of fun if you come!!! :)
item.name: 5th Annual Yule Party!
